<li>May this year bring you closer to your dreams and aspirations.</li>
<li>Have a wonderful birthday filled with love and laughter.</li>
<li>May Allah answer all your prayers this year.</li>
<li>Enjoy your special day, surrounded by the ones you love.</li>
<li>Sending you warm wishes and heartfelt prayers on your birthday.</li>
<li>May Allah's grace and mercy be upon you always.</li>
    

